{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1389,"text":"So when I do my job, people hate me."},{"time":4786,"text":"In fact, the better I do my job,"},{"time":7340,"text":"the more people hate me."},{"time":9145,"text":"And no, I'm not a meter maid,"},{"time":11096,"text":"and I'm not an undertaker."},{"time":13130,"text":"I am a progressive, lesbian\ntalking head on Fox News."}]},{"cues":[{"time":17076,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":19163,"text":"So y'all heard that, right?\nJust to make sure, right?"},{"time":21679,"text":"I am a gay talking head on Fox News."},{"time":24906,"text":"I am going to tell you how I do it,"},{"time":26621,"text":"and the most important thing I've learned."}]},{"cues":[{"time":28842,"text":"So I go on television."},{"time":30544,"text":"I debate people who literally want\nto obliterate everything I believe in --"},{"time":34664,"text":"in some cases, who don't want\nme and people like me to even exist."},{"time":38877,"text":"It's sort of like Thanksgiving\nwith your conservative uncle"},{"time":42008,"text":"on steroids,"},{"time":43537,"text":"with a live television\naudience of millions."},{"time":46933,"text":"It's totally almost just like that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":49242,"text":"And that's just on air."},{"time":51387,"text":"The hate mail I get is unbelievable."},{"time":53671,"text":"Last week alone, I got 238\npieces of nasty email"},{"time":58801,"text":"and more hate tweets\nthan I can even count."},{"time":61718,"text":"I was called an idiot,\na traitor, a scourge,"},{"time":65107,"text":"a cunt and an ugly man,"},{"time":67715,"text":"and that was just in one email."}]},{"cues":[{"time":69377,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":72195,"text":"So what have I realized,"},{"time":74978,"text":"being on the receiving end\nof all this ugliness?"},{"time":77739,"text":"Well, my biggest takeaway"},{"time":79398,"text":"is that for decades, we've been focused\non political correctness,"},{"time":83633,"text":"but what matters more\nis emotional correctness."},{"time":87993,"text":"Let me give you a small example."},{"time":89842,"text":"I don't care if you call me a dyke.\nI really don't."},{"time":92687,"text":"I care about two things."},{"time":94070,"text":"One, I care that you spell it right."}]},{"cues":[{"time":96728,"text":"(Laughter) (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":101706,"text":"Just quick refresher, it's D-Y-K-E."},{"time":105358,"text":"You'd totally be surprised."},{"time":108247,"text":"And second, I don't care about the word,\nI care about how you use it."},{"time":111518,"text":"Are you being friendly?\nAre you just being naive?"},{"time":113997,"text":"Or do you really want\nto hurt me personally?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":117885,"text":"Emotional correctness\nis the tone, the feeling,"},{"time":122407,"text":"how we say what we say,"},{"time":124392,"text":"the respect and compassion\nwe show one another."},{"time":127751,"text":"And what I've realized\nis that political persuasion"},{"time":130424,"text":"doesn't begin with ideas or facts or data."},{"time":134335,"text":"Political persuasion begins\nwith being emotionally correct."}]},{"cues":[{"time":138680,"text":"So when I first went\nto go work at Fox News,"},{"time":141241,"text":"true confession,"},{"time":142718,"text":"I expected there to be marks in the carpet"},{"time":145384,"text":"from all the knuckle-dragging."},{"time":147930,"text":"That, by the way, in case you're paying\nattention, is not emotionally correct."},{"time":151630,"text":"But liberals on my side,"},{"time":155033,"text":"we can be self-righteous,\nwe can be condescending,"},{"time":158588,"text":"we can be dismissive of anyone\nwho doesn't agree with us."},{"time":161385,"text":"In other words, we can\nbe politically right"},{"time":164199,"text":"but emotionally wrong."},{"time":167068,"text":"And incidentally, that means that\npeople don't like us. Right?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":173087,"text":"Now here's the kicker."},{"time":175003,"text":"Conservatives are really nice."},{"time":177611,"text":"I mean, not all of them,"},{"time":179092,"text":"and not the ones who send me hate mail,"},{"time":180977,"text":"but you would be surprised."},{"time":182616,"text":"Sean Hannity is one of\nthe sweetest guys I've ever met."},{"time":186910,"text":"He spends his free time\ntrying to fix up his staff on blind dates,"},{"time":191089,"text":"and I know that if I ever had a problem,"},{"time":193187,"text":"he would do anything he could to help."},{"time":195896,"text":"Now, I think Sean Hannity\nis 99 percent politically wrong,"},{"time":201057,"text":"but his emotional correctness\nis strikingly impressive."},{"time":204458,"text":"And that's why people listen to him."},{"time":206460,"text":"Because you can't get\nanyone to agree with you"},{"time":209016,"text":"if they don't even listen to you first."},{"time":211792,"text":"We spend so much time\ntalking past each other"},{"time":214828,"text":"and not enough time talking\nthrough our disagreements."},{"time":217871,"text":"And if we can start to find\ncompassion for one another,"},{"time":221710,"text":"then we have a shot\nat building common ground."},{"time":225792,"text":"It actually sounds really hokey\nto say it standing up here,"},{"time":229284,"text":"but when you try to put it in practice,"},{"time":231487,"text":"it's really powerful."}]},{"cues":[{"time":233345,"text":"So someone who says they hate immigrants,"},{"time":236224,"text":"I try to imagine how scared they must be"},{"time":238687,"text":"that their community is changing\nfrom what they've always known."},{"time":241759,"text":"Or someone who says they\ndon't like teachers' unions,"},{"time":245237,"text":"I bet they're really devastated to see\ntheir kid's school going into the gutter,"},{"time":249031,"text":"and they're just looking\nfor someone to blame."},{"time":251879,"text":"Our challenge is to find\nthe compassion for others"},{"time":256130,"text":"that we want them to have for us."},{"time":258690,"text":"That is emotional correctness."}]},{"cues":[{"time":261737,"text":"I'm not saying it's easy."},{"time":263267,"text":"An average of, like, 5.6 times per day"},{"time":266341,"text":"I have to stop myself from responding\nto all of my hate mail"},{"time":269183,"text":"with a flurry of vile profanities."},{"time":271949,"text":"This whole finding compassion\nand common ground with your enemies thing"},{"time":278172,"text":"is kind of like a political-spiritual\npractice for me,"},{"time":281584,"text":"and I ain't the Dalai Lama."},{"time":284516,"text":"I'm not perfect,\nbut what I am is optimistic."},{"time":290381,"text":"Because I don't just get hate mail."},{"time":292791,"text":"I get a lot of really nice\nletters, lots of them."},{"time":296039,"text":"And one of my all-time favorites begins:"},{"time":298601,"text":"\"I am not a big fan\nof your political leanings"},{"time":301294,"text":"or your sometimes tortured logic,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":303569,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":307222,"text":"but I'm a big fan of you as a person.\""},{"time":310611,"text":"Now this guy doesn't\nagree with me -- yet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":313940,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":317456,"text":"But he's listening --"},{"time":319719,"text":"not because of what I said,\nbut because of how I said it."},{"time":323084,"text":"And somehow, even though we've never met,\nwe've managed to form a connection."},{"time":327083,"text":"That's emotional correctness,"},{"time":329313,"text":"and that's how we start the conversations"},{"time":332102,"text":"that really lead to change."}]},{"cues":[{"time":333962,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":335140,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}